  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Blumental kitchen serves local foods and a selection of Swiss specialities including meat fondues with wine pairings from their own cellar. </p>
<ul>
<li>Continental breakfast buffet </li>
<li>A La Carte three course dinner</li>
</ul>]]></cateringDescription>
