  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Blumental is located directly on Murren's traffic-free high street and just a two minutes walk to the Stechelberg and Schilthorn lifts. Combining the old with the new, the bedrooms mix traditional Swiss décor and furniture with modern bathroom facilities.</p>
<p>The hotel restaurant makes classic Swiss dishes and has a great selection of wines from their own cellar, and staff are always happy to make pairing suggestions with your meal.</p>
<p>To make your stay in <a data-udi="umb://document/c494e0deab1140028dfcdd140d9451cc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c494e0deab1140028dfcdd140d9451cc}" title="Murren">Murren</a> extra special, the hotel includes a James Bond Brunch in the Piz Gloria once per stay per guest. L<span>ocated 2,970 metres above sea level at the </span>Schilthorn summit, the famous Piz Gloria rotating restaurant was used in the 1969 James Bond film 'On Her Majesty's Secret Service'. With spectacular snowy views of the Eiger, Mönch and Jungfrau, there is no better way to see the Jungfrau region. </p>]]></description>
